version_description:
It's summer! And we have a new update with which you can continue playing your favorite soccer game

New privacy pop up
Now you can see the percentage of charge on the loading screen
Amazing week offers
Maintenance
Bug fixing

We are starting the 2020/2021 soccer season with great enthusiasm and we want to present you the following news:

*U23 National Teams
*New alert messages
*Tutorials on the Tactic Cards
*Maintenance
*Bug fixing

The stadiums are ready, we have turned on the lights on the field, we have cut the grass and cleaned the benches.
Everything is ready for the new update:

*The bug of the league names in the season awards panel has been fixed
*Several players with the same number on the jersey error is fixed
*Sound bugs fixed
*Maintenance

We are in February! The month of love for football

We have a new update:

Graphical shadows improvements
We have updated the name of the app
Fixed a bug with displaying daily reward videos
Bug fixing
